1
00:00:00,250 --> 00:00:01,380
Hey, everyone~!

2
00:00:01,380 --> 00:00:03,210
Hello, everyone~!

3
00:00:03,210 --> 00:00:04,460
(Cheering)

4
00:00:04,460 --> 00:00:07,880
Alright, let's kick things off
with the Princess Pageant!

5
00:00:07,880 --> 00:00:10,680
(Cheering)

6
00:00:11,340 --> 00:00:14,040
(After Natsu-san helped me get ready,
she just disappeared.)

7
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:16,100
(So I'm on my own now...?)

8
00:00:16,100 --> 00:00:18,390
(I'm starting to get nervous...)

9
00:00:20,850 --> 00:00:23,150
Motomiya-kun!

10
00:00:23,150 --> 00:00:24,770
Mizukuchi-san?

11
00:00:24,770 --> 00:00:28,490
You startled me! You look so handsome!

12
00:00:28,490 --> 00:00:30,700
Thanks.

13
00:00:30,700 --> 00:00:36,120
It's because I said I like 'princely types,'
right?

14
00:00:36,830 --> 00:00:38,410
Oh...

15
00:00:38,410 --> 00:00:41,880
(Now that she mentions it, I think she did say that...)

16
00:00:41,880 --> 00:00:45,380
So, I have a favor to ask you.

17
00:00:45,380 --> 00:00:47,420
A favor?

18
00:00:48,050 --> 00:00:54,180
The person who's chosen as 'Prince' each year
always confesses to the person they like, right?

19
00:00:54,180 --> 00:00:56,180
Oh, you mean during the interview?

20
00:00:56,180 --> 00:01:00,440
Right! So...
if you become the Prince, Motomiya-kun...

21
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:03,440
Could you confess to me one more time?

22
00:01:04,270 --> 00:01:07,400
I promise I'll say yes this time.
